# Form Builder Project Overview

This is a Next.js application with Supabase integration for backend services. The project is structured as a form builder with admin capabilities and role-based access control.

## Key Files and Directories

- [middleware.ts](mdc:middleware.ts): Handles authentication and route protection
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx): Main application layout
- [lib/supabase/sql](mdc:lib/supabase/sql): SQL definitions for database tables
- [components/ui](mdc:components/ui): UI components using Shadcn UI

## Project Structure

- `app/`: Next.js application routes
  - `(admin)/`: Admin-only routes (protected)
  - `(public)/`: Public-facing routes
  - `api/`: API endpoints
- `components/`: Reusable React components
- `lib/`: Utility functions and libraries
- `hooks/`: Custom React hooks

